\/10\/GoTriple-Hackathon-Nov21_OPEN-CALL.pdf\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Screenshot-2021-10-11-165850.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1781\" width=\"71\" height=\"82\"\/><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For more information about the Hackathon, go to the event web page: <a href=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/gotriple-hackathon-2021\/\">https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/gotriple-hackathon-2021\/<\/a>  \u2013 register today and join a  <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/hashtag\/GoTripleHackathon\/\">#GoTripleHackathon<\/a> team!<\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>We invite programmers, librarians and researchers with programming skills, repository managers and non-IT specialists who work with managing vocabularies to the first GoTriple Hackathon to improve the coverage of the&nbsp;Library of Congress Subject Headings (LCSH)&nbsp;in the vocabulary of the discovery<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":1750,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[22,4,8],"tags":[21],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1748"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1748"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1748\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1785,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1748\/revisions\/1785"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/